meanings: elimination, deletion, striking out, expurgation, erasure, cancelation, 삭제하다 eliminate, remove, cancel, delete, strike[cross] out, expurgate, erase

vlive.korean: [진 거는 진 거니까 바로 삭제한 게 진짜 진심으로 대단] 아이디 바로...
vlive.english: [It's admirable that he erased his ID as soon as he lost] I erased my ID right away...
Muscle castle. - Isn't it muscle delete?

vlive.korean: 구독자는 뭐 그 사람이 계정 삭제했을 수도 있고...
vlive.english: As for that subscriber, he or she could have deleted the account.

vlive.korean: [꼬무리 언니와 함께해요!] 트러블 흔적을 삭제해주는 무결점 메이크업도 들고 왔으니까!
vlive.english: and show you a makeup style that shows flawless skin!

examples.english: Certain passages were excised from the book.

examples.korean: 그가 그 원고에서 몇 군데를 삭제했다.
examples.english: He made several deletions to the manuscript.
Strike her name off the list.

examples.korean: 내 이름은 그 명단에서 삭제되어 있었다.
examples.english: My name had been taken off the list.

examples.korean: 불쾌감을 줄 수 있는 그 단락은 삭제되었다.
